Musician, Peter Okoye is living the best time of his life as he took to social media to show off his second home in the US. Popular Nigerian singer, Peter Okoye has taken to social media to show off the interior of his second home in Atlanta. Peter Okoye better known as  Mr P while sharing the photos captioned it:  “ATLANTA… My second home sweet home #WelcomeToAtlanta.”  Source